<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个公主到十五岁生日时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她就可以游上去，看到地上世界。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她会告诉姐妹们她看到了什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当最大的公主满十五岁时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33341</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在海边呆了一阵子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我躺在月光下的沙滩上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>望着一个远远的城市。”她告诉妹妹们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49974</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些房子灯光闪烁，铃声隐隐地从高塔上传来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二年，第二个公主在日落时分游了上去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看见了金色的海水和红色的天空。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看见了软绵绵的紫色云彩，高高地挂在我头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有海面上一群白天鹅飞向夕阳。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下一年，第三个公主更加深入了地上世界。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我沿着河游泳，看见了起伏的山岭和有着高大绿树的树林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我听见鸟儿在给孩子们唱幸福的歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我还看到了没有尾巴的人类在海里游泳！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第三个公主被人类吓得游回了宽广的大海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>听了这件事，第四个公主失去了勇气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一直离陆地很远，只呆在汹涌的波涛里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看见调皮的海豚在海面上跳上跳下。”她对姐妹们说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“巨大的鲸鱼从背上的洞里喷水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>远远地，我看见了很多船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船离得很远，看起来像海鸥。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在轮到第五个了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的生日在冬天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>冬天时，大海会变成深绿色，而且暴风雨猛烈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巨大的冰山浮出了水面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我坐在一座冰山上，看见一艘船经过。”第五个公主对姐姐说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很快，大海变得波涛汹涌，绿色的波涛变成了黑色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雷声轰鸣，我看见闪电划过了天空！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天晚上，五个姐姐们一起游到了海面上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们坐在岩石上，向船唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们的声音很美丽，响彻天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，当船员听见姐妹们的歌声时，他们很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船员们马上改变船的方向。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几年过去了，人们开始讲唱歌人鱼的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们说人鱼们很邪恶，因为人鱼想欺骗人类。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们还说愚蠢的船员们喜欢听人鱼们唱歌，会把船开得很近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们的船会撞到岩石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但这些故事都不是真的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>姐妹们不想伤害任何人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们只是爱唱歌而已！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>五个公主最后对地上世界失去了兴趣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224233</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们越来越少地向船唱歌了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>对人鱼来说，没有地方比得上他们海底的家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>海底王国永远都是最适宜居住的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>五年里，小美人鱼听姐姐们讲故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她渴望自己到地上世界的冒险。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，好希望我已经十五岁了。”她渴望地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会爱上地上世界和那里的人类！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>